-- HSBC Mexico Sees 4th-Quarter Results Improving
-- B y   J o s e   E n r i q u e   A r r i o j a
-- 2012-12-05T00:17:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-05/hsbc-mexico-sees-4th-quarter-results-improving-correct-.html
HSBC Holdings Plc (HSBA) ’s  Mexico  unit
expects fourth-quarter results to be better than the bank’s
performance in previous quarters, Chief Executive Officer Luis
Pena Kegel said.  The lender is committed to be the third-largest corporate
debt seller in Mexico, Pena Kegel told reporters today in Mexico
City. Mexico’s economy will expand 4 percent this year, Pena
Kegel added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jose Enrique Arrioja in Mexico City at 
